alerts.description: ...HEAT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM EDT THIS EVENING... The National Weather Service in Mount Holly has issued a Heat Advisory, which is in effect until 7 PM EDT this evening. * HEAT INDEX VALUES...Around 100 degrees, due to temperatures in the lower 90s and dewpoints in the mid 70s. * TIMING...The heat index values will peak through about mid afternoon, then gradually lower through this evening. * IMPACTS...The heat and humidity may cause heat stress during outdoor exertion or extended exposure.
alerts.title: Heat Advisory
